<plot>House is a found footage experimental film. It uses an archival 50's nuclear testing film from the Prelinger archives and reclaims it by re-editing sound and image. Rooted in French 20's surrealism and 80's industrial music, House evokes the sense of displaced home and space in a globalized world of divided wealth and poverty.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?247371</url></doc>
